## 📞 THE DEMO FLOW (30 minutes)

---

## PHASE 1: Discovery & Pain (5-7 minutes)

### Opening (Build Rapport)
> *"Hey [Name], thanks for taking the time. Before I show you TIDY, I'd love to understand your current setup - that way I can make sure this is actually a good fit. Sound good?"*

### Key Discovery Questions:

#### 1. **Current Situation**
> *"What's your current property management setup?"*

**Listen for:**
- Self-managed? Using a PM? Which one?
- Pain points: cost, time, quality, communication
- Satisfaction level

#### 2. **Portfolio Size**
> *"How many properties do you manage?"*

**Why this matters:** ROI calculation + qualification

#### 3. **Revenue (CRITICAL)**
> *"What's your average revenue per property per year?"*

**If they don't know:**
> *"Ballpark is fine - is it closer to $30k? $50k? $100k?"*

**Why this matters:** This is your ROI calculator input

#### 4. **Current Costs**
> *"What are you paying now for property management?"*

**Typical responses:**
- Traditional PM: 25-30%
- Evolve/Guestable: 10-20%
- DIY: *"I do it myself"* → Ask: *"What's your time worth?"*

#### 5. **Biggest Frustration**
> *"What's the biggest frustration with your current setup?"*

**Let them vent. Take notes. Use this later.**

**Common pain points:**
- Too expensive
- Poor communication
- Cleaning quality issues
- Maintenance delays
- No transparency
- Too much of my time

---

### Transition to Pitch:
> *"Got it - so you've got [X] properties, averaging about $[X]k/year each, and you're with [current PM] paying around [X]%. And your biggest issue is [their pain point]. Does that sound right?"*

**Wait for confirmation.**

> *"Perfect. Let me show you how TIDY is different - and I'll walk you through the exact numbers for your portfolio. Fair?"*

---

## PHASE 2: The Hook (2-3 minutes)

### The Opening Statement
> *"Here's the core idea: What if you could replace your [25-30% traditional PM / 10-15% Evolve / DIY headaches] with AI + human experts for just 3.9%?"*

**Pause. Let it land.**

### The Quick Proof
> *"We've been doing this for 12 years. We've managed over 100,000 properties, 1.5 million units. We know short-term rentals inside and out."*

> *"But here's what makes us different: We use 15+ AI agents that handle 90% of the routine work - scheduling, coordination, vendor management, guest communication. Then we have 24/7 human concierge backup for the 10% that needs judgment."*

> *"The result? We can do everything a traditional property manager does - for a fraction of the cost."*

### Transition:
> *"Let me show you what that looks like for your properties specifically."*

---

## PHASE 3: The ROI Reveal (5 minutes)

**Pull up calculator or do live math on their specific numbers.**

### Example: 3 properties × $50k revenue each

> *"So on your portfolio, you're currently paying around $45,000 a year to your property manager, right?"*

**(Show the math):**

| Item | Traditional PM | TIDY | Your Savings |
|------|---------------|------|--------------|
| **Annual Revenue** | $150,000 | $150,000 | - |
| **PM Fee** | 30% = $45,000 | 3.9% = $5,850 | **$39,150/year** |
| **Your Net** | $105,000 | $144,150 | **+37% profit** |

> *"With TIDY, that becomes $5,850. You save $39,150 annually."*

**Pause. Let them absorb this.**

> *"What would you do with an extra $39k per year?"*

---

### Alternative: Comparing to Evolve/Guestable

| Item | Evolve (15%) | TIDY (3.9%) | Savings |
|------|-------------|-------------|---------|
| **Revenue** | $150,000 | $150,000 | - |
| **PM Fee** | $22,500* | $5,850 | **$16,650** |

*\*Plus 10% on cleaning fees (another $2-3k)*

> *"Even compared to the 'low-fee' platforms like Evolve, you're saving $16,000+ per year with TIDY."*

> *"That's not a small difference - that's a new property down payment every year."*

---

## PHASE 4: How It Works (5-7 minutes)

**Walk through the service - address their specific pain points.**

### 1. AI + Human Hybrid

> *"Here's how it works: We have 15+ AI agents running 24/7. They handle:"*
- Guest communication (inquiries, bookings, check-ins, check-outs)
- Cleaner scheduling and coordination
- Maintenance vendor dispatch
- Pricing optimization
- Quality control checks

> *"Then we have human concierges on standby 24/7 for anything the AI can't handle - unusual requests, judgment calls, escalations."*

> *"So you get the efficiency of automation with the intelligence of humans. Best of both worlds."*

---

### 2. What We Actually Do

**Tailor based on their current situation:**

#### If coming from **Traditional PM:**
> *"We do everything your current PM does - listings, pricing, guest vetting, cleaning, maintenance, guest communication - but at 3.9% instead of 30%."*

#### If coming from **Evolve/Self-Managed:**
> *"Unlike Evolve where you're still coordinating cleaners and handling maintenance yourself, we do ALL of that for you. You're truly hands-off."*

#### If coming from **Guestable:**
> *"Same hands-off experience, but at 3.9% instead of 15-20%. Plus faster payment and our profit guarantee."*

---

### Core Services (All Included at 3.9%):

✅ **Listing & Marketing**
- Listing creation & optimization (Airbnb, VRBO, Booking.com)
- Professional photography (you own the photos)
- Dynamic pricing optimization

✅ **Guest Management**
- Guest screening & communication
- 24/7 guest support
