---

### 3. Digital Twin Intelligence

> *"We also create a 'digital twin' of each property - basically a smart profile that learns the quirks of your place."*

> *"This helps us optimize everything from pricing to maintenance schedules to guest instructions. It gets smarter over time."*

---

### 4. Smart Pro Search

> *"We have a vetted network of thousands of local vendors - cleaners, handymen, contractors."*

> *"Our AI matches the right pro to each job based on location, availability, ratings, and price."*

> *"You don't source vendors. You don't negotiate. You don't chase them down. We handle all of it."*

