## PHASE 5: The Guarantee (3 minutes)

**This is your closer - neither Evolve nor Guestable has this.**

> *"Now here's the part that makes this a no-brainer..."*

> *"We guarantee you'll make MORE profit with TIDY than your current setup. Not the same. More."*

> *"If at any point you're not making more money with us than you were before - whether that's because of pricing, occupancy, whatever - we credit you the difference."*

> *"Zero risk. You literally cannot lose."*

**Pause.**

> *"Have you ever heard a property manager say that before?"*

*(Spoiler: They haven't.)*

> *"That's because most PMs are just trying to get their fee. We only win if you win. Our incentives are aligned."*

---

## PHASE 6: Handle Objections (5-7 minutes)

**Address objections as they come up - see [OBJECTION-HANDLING.md](./OBJECTION-HANDLING.md) for full responses.**

### Most Common Objections:

1. **"I need to think about it"**
2. **"How do I know the AI won't screw things up?"**
3. **"What about cleaning quality?"**
4. **"I like having control"**
5. **"Too expensive to switch"**
6. **"How is 3.9% sustainable? What's the catch?"**

**Key principle:** Don't dodge. Address directly and confidently.

---

## PHASE 7: The Close (3-5 minutes)

### Trial Close (if interested but hesitant):
> *"Based on what we've talked about - saving $[X] per year, fully hands-off, profit guarantee - does this feel like a good fit for you?"*

**If YES:**
> *"Awesome. Let's talk next steps. We can usually get you onboarded in 1-2 weeks. When would you want to start seeing that extra cash flow?"*

**If "I need to talk to my partner/think about it":**
> *"Fair enough. How about this: I'll send you a recap email with your specific numbers - the $[X] savings, the service breakdown, the guarantee details."*

> *"Let's schedule a quick 15-minute follow-up call in [3 days / next week] to answer any questions that come up. Does [day/time] work?"*

**If "I want to compare other options":**
> *"Smart move. Who else are you looking at?"*

**(If Evolve/Guestable):**
> *"Great options. Just make sure to ask them:"*
- *"What's your total fee including cleaning charges?"*
- *"Do you guarantee I'll make more profit?"*
- *"How fast do I get paid?"*

> *"Then compare apples to apples. I'm confident TIDY will come out ahead. Let me know what you find."*

---

### Hard Close (if clearly ready):
> *"So here's what happens next:"*

1. *"I'll send you the service agreement - it's straightforward, no surprises."*
2. *"We'll do a property walkthrough (virtual or in-person) to understand your setup."*
3. *"We'll connect to your existing listings OR create new ones from scratch."*
4. *"We'll introduce you to your account manager."*
5. *"Two weeks from now, you're hands-off and making more money."*

> *"Sound good? Any questions before we get started?"*

