## ✅ Demo Checklist

### Before the Call:
- [ ] Research prospect (Close.com)
- [ ] Calculate their estimated savings
- [ ] Have deck/calculator ready
- [ ] Clear calendar (not rushed)

### During the Call:
- [ ] Let them talk first (discovery)
- [ ] Use their numbers (not generic examples)
- [ ] Address their specific pain points
- [ ] Pause after the guarantee (let it sink in)
- [ ] Handle objections directly (don't dodge)
- [ ] Ask for the close

### After the Call:
- [ ] Send recap email within 1 hour
- [ ] Log call notes in Close.com
- [ ] Set follow-up task/reminder
- [ ] Update lead status

