## 🎭 Tonality & Style

### DO:
✅ Be consultative (ask questions, listen)  
✅ Use their specific numbers  
✅ Show confidence in the product  
✅ Make it conversational (not scripted)  
✅ Let pauses breathe (don't rush)  

### DON'T:
❌ Be pushy or aggressive  
❌ Use jargon or tech-speak  
❌ Trash competitors (position TIDY as better, not them as bad)  
❌ Promise features that don't exist  
❌ Ramble - be concise  

